title: 67. The Leadership Paradox
itunes:title: 67. The Leadership Paradox
description: Vince Lombardi was right, "Leading by example isn't the best way to lead; it's the only way to lead." However, if you want to create a legacy for decades to come, there's another part. On today's episode, Andy talks about the second part needed to be an effective leader.
